Package com.edugility.jpa.converters

Provides classes and interfaces implementing the AttributeConverter interface.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BooleanToShortConverter
    An AttributeConverter that converts a Boolean to and from a Short representation.
    ClassToStringConverter
    An AttributeConverter that converts a Class to and from its String representation.
    LocaleToLanguageTagConverter
    An AttributeConverter that converts a Locale to and from its language tag representation.
